        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> The Aug of Death spell gives a haste which is about 5% less than SoS. It also bumps some stats. You may not notice a hell of a functional difference on the 53rd pet, but on the 56th pet, it's damn amazing. It lasts a decent time also, although it does cost a decent whack of mana and takes a while to cast, normally OK in down time, but on the field the damage loss is noticeable, at least with my focussed monk pet.</P><P>2K seems a bit much, but on my server, every spell before 56th sells for about 200 PP, which is what I bought my 53rd pet, Sacrifice, Aug of Death and the like for. It's a good spell, but personally, I wouldn't pay for more than 1K for it, and even then, it's pretty darn harsh. But, servers change, and it depends on how many spell farmers and guilds you have on yours, Rodcet Nife has a lot of them, so spell prices are semi cheap.</P><P>Skin of the Shadow is wonderful, guaranteed invis that you can use anywhere and now anytime. The strange vision component takes a lil time getting used to, but having a stable invis is so nice now. Levant rocks for getting over zones, or sometimes just out of zones, such as going over SG or getting outta Velks.</P><P>NOTE ON "SAFE" ZONES: VI has a strange idea of "safe" for Levant. The safe zone in OOT is Sister Island, which every necromancer is KOS at, and the safe zone in Gfay is awfully near Kelethin. I would advise casting this zone with care so you don't kill yourself when you pop in. I got stuffed here when I gated while being ported (don't do this) in OOT, and not having a shard at the Gfay spires when it sent people up. Just be paranoid, it's the necro way :P</P><P>Will also agree with Bren that do fill your spellbook as much as you can, just for the sake of it. However, don't send yourself to the poorhouse over it.</P><P>/em tries to get her Demi Lich for 3K again :P (yeah, right :P)</P><P>Saminga Daemonregina, 58th Bad Girl of Rodcet Nife.</P><P>Good girls go to Heaven, bad girls FD and /q out.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
